<section class="matsato-section">
  <div class="matsato-container">
    <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 50px;">
      <h2 class="matsato-title">When tradition meets modern design</h2>
      <p class="matsato-subtitle">Techniques passed on through generations</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 40px;">
      <div class="matsato-benefit-card" style="text-align: left; background: none; box-shadow: none; padding: 0;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--matsato-accent-color); font-size: 1.4rem;">In love with the art of knife making</h3>
        <p>Matsato knives were created out of passion for the art of cooking. We wanted to revolutionise the market by being the first to ever create a specialised Kitchen Knife with a unique blade.</p>
        <p>Traditional Japanese knife making techniques combined with modern approach resulted in this fabulous Matsato santoku knife.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="matsato-benefit-card" style="text-align: left; background: none; box-shadow: none; padding: 0;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--matsato-accent-color); font-size: 1.4rem;">Sharpness vs. Comfort - why not have it all?</h3>
        <p>Some knives are sharp, but come with the cost of being fragile and prone to chipping and oxidation.</p>
        <p>We believe real kitchen chef should never have such problems. Matsato knife is extremely sturdy and sharp. Quality stainless steel and beech handle guarantees great performance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 50px; text-align: center;">
      <img src="{{ section.settings.image | image_url: width: 1200 }}" alt="Matsato Tradition" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Matsato Brand Story",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image",
      "label": "Large Story Image"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Matsato Brand Story"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
